milestones.description: Jayasuriya has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (72) in an innings in ODIs for SL, going past de Silva's 60
Jayasuriya's 140 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SL), surpassing Roy Dias's 121
Jayasuriya has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (6) in ODIs for SL, going past de Silva's 4
